<span id="freeTextContainer12321263756171512943">I thought I would like this book more but it just didn&apos;t grab me as much as I thought it would . There&apos;s some lovely writing but what should have been a beautiful love story for me was a bit shallow. More like 2 &amp; 1/2 stars.</span>
